talkie-1930-13b-it-q5

This repository packages an experimental Q5_0 GGUF derived from Talkie 1930
13B IT, plus a local Node chat app and patched llama.cpp runtime notes.

Upstream Talkie project:
https://github.com/talkie-lm/talkie

Talkie authors named in the upstream README:
Alec Radford, Nick Levine, and David Duvenaud.

Upstream llama.cpp project:
https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp

The GGUF is not currently compatible with stock llama.cpp or stock LM Studio.
It requires the Talkie architecture support described in this repository.
